                     <interp inst="t17830115-60-off339" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17830115-60-cd340" type="crimeDate">5th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17830115-60-off339 t17830115-60-cd340"></join> instant, two silk gowns, value 3 l. one black silk cloak laced, value, 12 s. two linen gowns, value 15 s. three muslin aprons, value 9 s. three muslin handkerchiefs, value 6 s. one laced muslin cap, value 15 d. one linen shift, value 2 s. one pair of cotton stockings, value 6 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17830115-60-victim638" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Chapman
