                  : one silk handkerchief, value 12 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17830115-60-victim640" type="victimName">
                           Matthia 
                           Drewitt
                        <interp inst="t17830115-60-victim640" type="surname" value="Drewitt"></interp>
